{"tid":858942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★港豬DNA】冇得返工 即變勇武---不甘遭解僱　麵包師傅刑恐前僱主囚6月","createTime":"2018-10-12T07:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T05:41:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2e2a066862e8c6d5fcc9b37bb2bc8cbcf94399","tid":858942,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"25歲青年黃家恩涉寄𠝹刀恐嚇信到屯門裁判法院和前僱主案，今日(12日)在粉嶺法院再訊，經新增控罪後，黃被控11項刑事恐嚇罪，其中2項涉及法院和裁判官的控罪暫毋須答辯，押後至下月1日轉介到區院再訊，至於餘下9項涉及其前僱主的控罪，他則認罪，判囚6個月。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告原本在山崎麵包任麵包師傅，今年5月被解僱。其後山崎麵包的2間分店，於今年7月共9度收到內附火機、𠝹刀和生果刀等的信件，其中一封信更附有「欠債還錢，天經地義」的紙條，店方於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181012/bkn-20181012133334822-1012_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181012%2Fbkn-20181012133334822-1012_00822_001.html&d=6JrVqrMZ%2BG20ESSJulJ3SI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=cab5957c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181012/bkn-20181012133334822-1012_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8088197bcc9dd96688d78658b931b99719994599","tid":858942,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:07:20.000Z","msg":"港pig進入 暴走mode 唯一方法"},{"pid":"b74eb6bafdddb16d2103b7b02daf922882973996","tid":858942,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54421aec93f12c703f9ada6b4e6321dfc8650e0f","tid":858942,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:41:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}